### 결제 요청
POST {{commerce-api}}/api/v1/orders/321321/pay
Content-Type: application/json
X-Loopers-LoginId: user123
X-Loopers-LoginPw: Password1!

{
  "cardType": "SAMSUNG",
  "cardNo": "1234-5678-9012-3456"
}

### 결제 요청 (KB 카드)
POST {{commerce-api}}/api/v1/orders/1/pay
Content-Type: application/json
X-Loopers-LoginId: user123
X-Loopers-LoginPw: Password1!

{
  "cardType": "KB",
  "cardNo": "1234-5678-9012-3456"
}

### 결제 요청 (HYUNDAI 카드)
POST {{commerce-api}}/api/v1/orders/1/pay
Content-Type: application/json
X-Loopers-LoginId: user123
X-Loopers-LoginPw: Password1!

{
